<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="english">
  <%- include('header') %>
  <body>
    <!-- navbar with BOOOTSTRAP -->
    <%- include('navbar') %>

    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center flex-column mb-5 py-5">
      <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 mb-3">
        <h2 class="title-pink">
          Snap photos of your clothes and share like never before
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="row my-3">
        <!-- Card1 -->
        <div class="card col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 border-0 p-3">
          <img
            height="250px"
            class="card-img-top rounded-0 object-fit-cover"
            src="/assets/Page7/Bird's view shoot.jpg"
            alt="Card image cap"
          />
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title text-center">Goddess in Purple</h5>
            <p class="card-text plain-text">
              The woman in the photo is wearing a flowing purple dress that
              cascades over her body like a waterfall. The dress is made of a
              light, breathable fabric that softly drapes over her curves. The
              vibrant shade of purple complements her skin tone and exudes
              confidence and...
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card2 -->
        <div class="card col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 border-0 p-3">
          <img
            height="250px"
            class="card-img-top rounded-0 object-fit-cover"
            src="/assets/Page7/blonde-lady.jpg"
            alt="Card image cap"
          />
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title text-center">Wrapped in Nature's Beauty</h5>
            <p class="card-text plain-text">
              The woman in the photo exudes a sense of effortless style as she
              stands in an outdoor setting, adorned with a colorful scarf. Her
              fashion sense is both bohemian and chic, with a focus on natural,
              earthy tones and textures. The scarf she wears is made of a soft.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card3 -->
        <div class="card col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 border-0 p-3">
          <img
            height="250px"
            class="card-img-top rounded-0 object-fit-fill"
            src="/assets/Page7/Clutching self.jpg"
            alt="Card image cap"
          />
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title text-center">In the Embrace of Elegance</h5>
            <p class="card-text plain-text">
              The woman in the photo exudes grace and sophistication as she
              clutches a sheer drape in her hand. Her fashion sense is refined
              and elegant, with a focus on classic styles and clean lines.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row my-3">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
          <h2 class="d-inline">The largest community of fashion enthusiasts</h2>
          <div class="d-inline mx-3">
            <button
              id="play-button"
              onclick="playVideo()"
              class="d-inline btn btn-primary shadow rounded-circle d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center border-0"
              onclick="playVideo()"
            >
              <img src="/assets/Page7/Polygon.png" />
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row my-3">
        <video controls autoplay>
          <source
            src="/assets/Page7/Clothes colection video.mp4"
            type="video/mp4"
          />
          Your browser does not support HTML video.
        </video>
      </div>

      <div class="row my-3">
        <h3 class="title-pink text-center mt-5">You're in good company</h3>
        <h5 class="text-center my-2">View what other users have uploaded</h5>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-4 col-md-2 my-2">
            <img class="w-100 h-100" src="/assets/Page7/fashion-girl.jpg" />
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-2 my-2">
            <img class="w-100 h-100" src="/assets/Page7/Fur coat.jpg" />
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-2 my-2">
            <img class="w-100 h-100" src="/assets/Page7/girl-bridge.jpg" />
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-2 my-2">
            <img class="w-100 h-100" src="/assets/Page7/hijab.jpg" />
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-2 my-2">
            <img class="w-100 h-100" src="/assets/Page7/Leaning on wall.jpg" />
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-2 my-2">
            <img class="w-100 h-100" src="/assets/Page7/Orange coat.jpg" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- footer with Bootstrap -->
    <%- include('footer') %>

    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-oBqDVmMz9ATKxIep9tiCxS/Z9fNfEXiDAYTujMAeBAsjFuCZSmKbSSUnQlmh/jp3"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-heAjqF+bCxXpCWLa6Zhcp4fu20XoNIA98ecBC1YkdXhszjoejr5y9Q77hIrv8R9i"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/mainScript.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
